T* (The UHD driver includes example programs that can verify receiver operation.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Example RX1 command:) Tj
T* (/usr/local/lib/uhd/examples/rx_ascii_art_dft --freq 88.1e6 --rate 1e6 --gain 70 --ref-lvl) Tj
T* (-30 --subdev "A:0" --ant RX1) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (To test RX2, change the antenna flag to RX2 and the subdevice spec to A:1.) Tj
T* (Type Q or Ctrl-C to stop rx_ascii_art_dft.) Tj
T* () Tj
